---
title: John Dory Fish & Basil Pesto Potatoes with Feta & Sautéed Greens
description: There’s no need to wait in line for the perfect piece of dory, fresh off the boat because you can serve it up right now, seared and blushing
with a side of potatoes sprinkled in feta for a touch of salty creaminess. Add a drizzle of basil pesto because every fish needs a kiss from
fresh herbs - that’s why it’s blushing pink!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/john-dory-fish-basil-pesto-potatoes-285a18d7.jpg
